<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>true</action_update><active>false</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>sn_hiring_feedback_interview</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>InterviewerInvitation</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/ ) {

    // Add your code here
    var sysId = current.getUniqueValue();
    var interviewsGr = new GlideRecord('sn_hiring_feedback_interview');
    interviewsGr.get(sysId);
    if (current.isNewRecord()) {
        var user = new GlideRecord('sys_user');
        user.get(current.interviewer_email);
        gs.eventQueue('sn_hiring_feedback.Interviewer_Invite', interviewsGr.interviewer_email.name, user.getValue('first_name'), current.job.candidate_name);
    } else if (current.interviewer_email != previous.interviewer_email) {
        var user = new GlideRecord('sys_user');
        user.get(current.interviewer_email);
        gs.eventQueue('sn_hiring_feedback.Interviewer_Invite', interviewsGr.interviewer_email.name, user.getValue('first_name'), current.job.candidate_name);
    }

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-04-24 11:34:31</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>2c9a804d538533004dc0ddeeff7b1280</sys_id><sys_mod_count>10</sys_mod_count><sys_name>InterviewerInvitation</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Hiring Feedback" source="sn_hiring_feedback">817f729837831300a128036973990e47</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Hiring Feedback">817f729837831300a128036973990e47</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_2c9a804d538533004dc0ddeeff7b1280</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2022-05-05 09:53:15</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=2c9a804d538533004dc0ddeeff7b1280"/></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sys_script_include_db82d172b70473008fee6f28ee11a9b9
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>sn_hiring_feedback.JobApplicantUploadUtil</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>false</client_callable><description>To upload job applicants using excel.</description><name>JobApplicantUploadUtil</name><script><![CDATA[var JobApplicantUploadUtil = Class.create();
JobApplicantUploadUtil.prototype = {
    IMPORT_TABLE: "sn_hiring_feedback_job_applicant_import_error",
    JOB_APPLICANT_TABLE: "sn_hiring_feedback_job",
    FIELDS_LOOKUP: {},

    /*
    	Stores columns of IMPORT TABLE
    */
    initialize: function() {
        var tab = new GlideRecord("sys_dictionary");
        tab.addQuery("name", this.IMPORT_TABLE);
        tab.addQuery("internal_type", "!=", "collection");
        tab.query();
        while (tab.next()) {
            var colLabel = (tab.getDisplayValue("column_label"));
            var colName = tab.getValue("element");
            if (!gs.nil(colLabel) && !gs.nil(colName))
                this.FIELDS_LOOKUP[colLabel.toLowerCase()] = colName;
        }
    },

    uploadExcel: function(excel, dataSource, import_set) {
        var import_count = 0;
        var applicantsCount = 0;
        var jobApplicantId = null;
        var reasons = [];
        var mandFields = [];

        var row = this._constructRow(new global.JSON().decode(excel));

        if (!this._isRowEmpty(row)) {

            row["data_source"] = dataSource;
            row["import_set"] = import_set;

            //Validating candidate name
            if (!this._checkAvailability(row, "candidate_name")) {
                this._addToList(mandFields, "Candidate Name");
                this._addToList(reasons, "Candidate Name not found");
            }
            // Validating candidate email
            if (!this._checkAvailability(row, "email")) {
                this._addToList(mandFields, "Candidate Email");
                this._addToList(reasons, "Candidate Email not found");
            } else if (this._isDuplicateApplicantEmail(row["email"])) {
                this._addToList(reasons, "Candidate email already exists");
            }
            // Validating Job ID
            if (!this._checkAvailability(row, "job")) {
                this._addToList(mandFields, "Job ID");
                this._addToList(reasons, "Job ID not found");
            }
            // Validating Manager Email and replacing it with his sys_id (if exists)
            if (!this._checkAvailability(row, "manager")) {
                this._addToList(mandFields, "Manager Email.");
                this._addToList(reasons, "Manager Email not found.");
            } else if (!this._isServiceNowEmail(row['manager'])) {
                this._addToList(reasons, "Manager email is not of ServiceNow");
                row['manager'] = '';
            } else {
                var managerSysID = this._getSysIDFromEmail(row['manager']);
                if (!managerSysID) {
                    this._addToList(reasons, "Manager's email is not registered");
                    row['manager'] = '';
                } else {
                    row['manager'] = managerSysID;
                }
            }

            // Validating Mobile Number
            if (!this._checkAvailability(row, "mobile")) {
                this._addToList(mandFields, "Mobile");
                this._addToList(reasons, "Mobile number not found");
            }
            // Validating Recruiter Email and replacing it with his sys_id (if exists)
            if (!this._checkAvailability(row, "recruiter")) {
                this._addToList(mandFields, "Recruiter");
                this._addToList(reasons, "Recruiter email not found.");
            } else if (!this._isServiceNowEmail(row['recruiter'])) {
                this._addToList(reasons, "Recruiter email is not of ServiceNow");
                row['recruiter'] = '';
            } else {
                var recruiterSysID = this._getSysIDFromEmail(row['recruiter']);
                if (!recruiterSysID) {
                    this._addToList(reasons, "Recruiter's email is not registered");
                    row['recruiter'] = '';
                } else {
                    row['recruiter'] = recruiterSysID;
                }
            }
            // Validating Team Name
            if (!this._checkAvailability(row, "team")) {
                this._addToList(mandFields, "Team");
                this._addToList(reasons, "Team not found");
            }
            // Validating Experience
            var experience = String(row['experience']).trim();
            if (experience) {
                var experienceRegex = /^[0-9]*\.?[0-9]*\+?$/;
                if (!experience.match(experienceRegex)) {
                    this._addToList(reasons, "Wrong Exp Format. Accepted: 12, 11.5, 10+, 7.8+");
                }
            }
            // Validating Job Role
            this.isJobRoleCorrect = true;
            var jobRole = row['job_role'];
            var jobRoleSysID = this._getJobRoleID(row["job_role"]);
            if (jobRoleSysID == 'not found') {
                this.isJobRoleCorrect = false;
                this._addToList(reasons, "Wrong Job Role mentioned");
            } else {
                row['job_role'] = jobRoleSysID;
            }
			//Validating Skills
			gs.error("Aaditya 123 3: Skills is " + row['u_skills']);
			if (this._checkAvailability(row, "u_skills")) {
				var skills = row["u_skills"].split(",");
				var skillsIds = this._getSkillIds(row["u_skills"]);
				row["u_skills"] = skillsIds.join(",");
			}
			
            // If reasons or mandatory fields are populated, createImportError
            if (reasons.length > 0 || mandFields.length > 0) {
                this._createImportError(row, reasons.join(", "), mandFields.join(", "));
                import_count = import_count + 1;
            } else {
                // Replacing Event name with Sys ID
                if (row["event"])
                    row["event"] = this._eventOperations(row["event"]);
                jobApplicantId = this._createJobApplicantRecord(row);

                applicantsCount = applicantsCount + 1;
            }
        }

        var ret = {
            "import_error_count": import_count,
            "job_applicant_count": applicantsCount,
            "job_applicant_id": jobApplicantId
        };
        return ret;
    },
    _getJobRoleID: function(jobRole) {
        var jobRoleGr = new GlideRecord('sn_hiring_feedback_job_role');
        jobRoleGr.addQuery('job_role', jobRole);
        jobRoleGr.query();
        if (jobRoleGr.hasNext()) {
            jobRoleGr.next();
            return jobRoleGr.getUniqueValue();
        } else {
            return 'not found';
        }
    },
    _constructRow: function(restRow) {
        var row = {};
        for (var key in restRow) {
            // Temporary Fix
            if (key == 'name') {
                row['candidate_name'] = restRow[key];
            }
            if (key == 'job role') {
                row['job_role'] = restRow[key];
            }
			if (key == 'skills') {
                row['u_skills'] = restRow['skills'];
            }
            gs.info(this.FIELDS_LOOKUP[key] + ' ' + restRow[key] + ' ' + key);
            row[this.FIELDS_LOOKUP[key]] = restRow[key];
        }
        return row;
    },

    _isRowEmpty: function(row) {
        var fields = [
            "email", "event", "candidate_name", "job", "company",
            "experience", "manager", "mobile", "recruiter",
            "status", "team", "job role"
        ];
        for (var prop in row) {
            if (!gs.nil(row[prop])) {
                if (fields.indexOf(prop) !== -1)
                    return false;
            }
        }
        return true;
    },

    _isDuplicateApplicantEmail: function(applicantEmail) {
        var jobApplicantsTable = new GlideRecord('sn_hiring_feedback_job');
        jobApplicantsTable.query("candidate_email", applicantEmail);
        jobApplicantsTable.setLimit(1);
        jobApplicantsTable.query();

        if (jobApplicantsTable.next()) {
            return true;
        } else {
            return false;
        }
    },

    /*
    	Adds errors reasons
    */
    _addToList: function(list, val) {
        if (!gs.nil(val)) {
            if (list.indexOf(val) === -1)
                list.push(val);
        }
        return;
    },

    /*
    	Inserts error rows in IMPORT TABLE
    */
    _createImportError: function(row, reasons, mandFields) {
        var fields = [
            "email", "event", "candidate_name", "job", "company",
            "experience", "manager", "mobile", "recruiter",
            "status", "team"
        ];

        var staging = new GlideRecord(this.IMPORT_TABLE);
        for (var i = 0; i < fields.length; i++) {
            var val = (gs.nil(row[fields[i]])) ? "" : row[fields[i]];
            staging.setValue(fields[i], val);
        }
        if (this.isJobRoleCorrect == true) {
            staging.setValue('job_role', row['job_role']);
        }
        staging.setValue("error_status", "open");
        staging.setValue("reason", reasons);
        staging.setValue("reason_list", mandFields);
        staging.setValue("import_set", row["import_set"]);
        staging.setValue("data_source", row["data_source"]);

        if (row["event"]) {
            staging.setValue("event_name", row["event"]);
        }

        return staging.insert();
    },

    _checkAvailability: function(row, field) {
        if (gs.nil(row[field]))
            return false;
        else
            return true;
    },

    /*
    	Inserts rows in JOB_APPLICANT_TABLE
    */
    _createJobApplicantRecord: function(row) {
        var jobApplicantsTable = new GlideRecord(this.JOB_APPLICANT_TABLE);

        jobApplicantsTable.setValue('candidate_email', row['email']);
        jobApplicantsTable.setValue('candidate_name', row['candidate_name']);
        jobApplicantsTable.setValue('event', row['event']);
        jobApplicantsTable.setValue('hiring_manager', row['manager']);
        jobApplicantsTable.setValue('hiring_team', row['team']);
        jobApplicantsTable.setValue('job_req_id', row['job']);
        jobApplicantsTable.setValue('recruiter', row['recruiter']);
        jobApplicantsTable.setValue('mobile', row['mobile']);
        jobApplicantsTable.setValue('company', row['company']);
        jobApplicantsTable.setValue('experience', row['experience']);
        jobApplicantsTable.setValue('job_role', row['job_role']);
		jobApplicantsTable.setValue('u_skills', row['u_skills']);

        return jobApplicantsTable.insert();
    },

    _isServiceNowEmail: function(email) {
        if (email.indexOf('@servicenow.com') == -1)
            return false;
        else
            return true;
    },

    /*
    	Creates new Event(if not found) and returns sys_id
    */
    _eventOperations: function(eventName) {
        var eventsTable = new GlideRecord('sn_hiring_feedback_event');
        eventsTable.addQuery('name', eventName);
        eventsTable.setLimit(1);
        eventsTable.query();

        if (eventsTable.next()) {
            return eventsTable.getUniqueValue();
        } else {
            eventsTable.setValue('name', eventName);
            return eventsTable.insert();
        }
    },

    _getSysIDFromEmail: function(email) {
        var sysUserGr = new GlideRecord('sys_user');
        var recordExists = sysUserGr.get('email', email);
        if (recordExists) {
            return sysUserGr.sys_id;
        } else {
            return false;
        }
    },
	_getSkillIds: function(skills) {
		var skillsIds = [];
		gs.error("Aaditya 123 1: Skills is " + skills);
		var skillsGr = new GlideRecord('sn_hiring_feedback_skills');
		skillsGr.addQuery('u_skill_name', 'IN', skills);
		skillsGr.query();
		while(skillsGr.next()){
			  skillsIds.push(skillsGr.sys_id);
		}
		gs.error("Aaditya 123 2: Skill ids is " + skillsIds.join(','));
		return skillsIds;
		
	},

    type: 'JobApplicantUploadUtil'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-03-11 10:51:40</sys_created_on><sys_id>db82d172b70473008fee6f28ee11a9b9</sys_id><sys_mod_count>85</sys_mod_count><sys_name>JobApplicantUploadUtil</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Hiring Feedback" source="sn_hiring_feedback">817f729837831300a128036973990e47</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Hiring Feedback">817f729837831300a128036973990e47</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_db82d172b70473008fee6f28ee11a9b9</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2022-05-04 09:23:17</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>sn_hiring_feedback.ZoomMeetingUtilsForInterview</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>false</client_callable><description/><name>ZoomMeetingUtilsForInterview</name><script><![CDATA[var ZoomMeetingUtilsForInterview = Class.create();
ZoomMeetingUtilsForInterview.prototype = {
    initialize: function() {},

    createMeeting: function() {
        var RESOURCE_PATH = '/api/snc/interview_zoom_meeting/getMeeting';

        var request = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2();
        request.setEndpoint('https://hidevidc.service-now.com/' + RESOURCE_PATH);

        request.setHttpMethod('POST'); //Eg. UserName="admin", Password="admin" for this code sample.var user = 'admin';var password = 'admin';
        //request.setBasicAuth(user,password);//If having any requestBody

        var requestBody = {
            "startDateTime": "2020-12-18 15:10:00",
            "agenda": 'Test',
            "topic": 'Interview'
        };

        request.setRequestBody(JSON.stringify(requestBody));

        request.setRequestHeader("Accept", "application/json");
        var response = request.execute();
        var responseJSON = JSON.parse(response.getBody());
        gs.info('MeetingLog - ' + response.getBody());
        if (responseJSON.result && responseJSON.result.join_url) {
            return responseJSON.result.join_url;
        } else {
            return '';
        }
    },
    createMeetings: function(eventId) {
        var RESOURCE_PATH = '/api/snc/interview_zoom_meeting/getMeetings';

        try {
            var request = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2();
            request.setEndpoint('https://hidevidc.service-now.com/' + RESOURCE_PATH);

            request.setHttpMethod('POST'); //Eg. UserName="admin", Password="admin" for this code sample.var user = 'admin';var password = 'admin';
            //request.setBasicAuth(user,password);//If having any requestBody

            var interviewIds = [];
            var interviewGr = new GlideRecord('sn_hiring_feedback_interview');

            interviewGr.addQuery('u_interview_event', eventId);
            interviewGr.query();

            while (interviewGr.next()) {
				interviewIds.push(interviewGr.sys_id + '');
            }

            if (interviewIds.length > 0) {
                var requestBody = {
                    "startDateTime": "2020-12-18 15:10:00",
                    "agenda": 'Servicenow Interview',
                    "topic": 'Event Name placeholder',
                    'event_id': eventId,
                    'interview_ids': interviewIds
                };

                request.setRequestBody(JSON.stringify(requestBody));
                request.setRequestHeader("Accept", "application/json");
                var response = request.execute();
                var responseJSON = JSON.parse(response.getBody());

                // Response is an Objs of form -
                // 			response : {
                // 				result : {
                // 					eventSysId : {
                // 						interviewSysId1 : {
                // 							{
				//	  						  join_url, meeting_id, start_url, success
				//							}
                // 						},
                // 						interviewSysId2 : {
                // 							meetingLink
                // 						},	
                // 					}
                // 				}
                // 			}
                var eventMeetingObj = responseJSON.result[eventId];

                interviewGr = new GlideRecord('sn_hiring_feedback_interview');
                interviewGr.addQuery('u_interview_event', eventId);
                interviewGr.query();

                while (interviewGr.next()) {
                    if (eventMeetingObj[interviewGr.sys_id + ''] && eventMeetingObj[interviewGr.sys_id + ''].success) {
                        var meetingObj = eventMeetingObj[interviewGr.sys_id + ''];
                        interviewGr.u_meeting_link = meetingObj.join_url;
                        interviewGr.update();
                    }
                }


            } else {
                gs.addErrorMessage('You have no interviews for the event!');
            }

            //         gs.info('MeetingLog - ' + response.getBody());
            //         if (response.result && response.result.join_url) {
            //             response.result.join_url;
            //         } else {
            //             return '';
            //         }
        } catch (err) {
            gs.addErrorMessage('Could not create meetings - ' + err);
			throw(err);
        }

    },

    type: 'ZoomMeetingUtilsForInterview'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>kaustubh.kislay@snc</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2022-05-04 13:16:11</sys_created_on><sys_id>59451449975385108ea0f73ef053afb9</sys_id><sys_mod_count>15</sys_mod_count><sys_name>ZoomMeetingUtilsForInterview</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Hiring Feedback" source="sn_hiring_feedback">817f729837831300a128036973990e47</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Hiring Feedback">817f729837831300a128036973990e47</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_59451449975385108ea0f73ef053afb9</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>kaustubh.kislay@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2022-05-05 05:36:36</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>

	var email = current.job.candidate_email;
	var state = current.getValue("interview_type");
	
	var grJob = new GlideRecord("sn_hiring_feedback_job_applicants");
    grJob.addQuery("u_job_applicant.candidate_email", email);

	if(grJob.next()) {
		grJob.u_state = state;
		grJob.update();
	}

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin1</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2022-05-04 19:34:47</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>c37a6d05979785108ea0f73ef053af40</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Update State in VTB board</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Hiring Feedback" source="sn_hiring_feedback">817f729837831300a128036973990e47</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Hiring Feedback">817f729837831300a128036973990e47</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_c37a6d05979785108ea0f73ef053af40</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2022-05-05 09:42:01</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=c37a6d05979785108ea0f73ef053af40"/></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="DELETE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>false</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>true</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>sn_hiring_feedback_temp_user</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>Update Temp User</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions>sn_hiring_feedback.recruiter</role_conditions><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/) {

	var sys_user_gr = new GlideRecord('sys_user');
	var userEmail = previous.user_id.toString();
	var userId = userEmail.substring(0, userEmail.indexOf('@'));
	
	var currentEmail = current.user_id.toString();
	var currentUserId = currentEmail.substring(0, currentEmail.indexOf('@'));
	
	sys_user_gr.addQuery('user_name', userId);
	sys_user_gr.setLimit(1);
	sys_user_gr.query();
	
	if(sys_user_gr.next()) {
		sys_user_gr.email = current.email;
		sys_user_gr.user_name = currentUserId;
		sys_user_gr.first_name = current.first_name;
		sys_user_gr.last_name = current.last_name;
		sys_user_gr.team = current.team;

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="DELETE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>true</action_delete><action_insert>false</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>false</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>sn_hiring_feedback_temp_user</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>Delete Temp User</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/) {

	// On delete from Temp User, delete from sys_user table too
	var sys_user_gr = new GlideRecord("sys_user");
	var userEmail =  current.user_id;
	var userID = userEmail.substring(0, userEmail.indexOf('@'));
	
	sys_user_gr.addQuery('user_name', userID);
	sys_user_gr.setLimit(1);
	sys_user_gr.query();
	
	if(sys_user_gr.next()) {
		sys_user_gr.deleteRecord();
	}

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-04-01 06:28:19</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>9e4ceca5532433004dc0ddeeff7b12e6</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Delete Temp User</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Hiring Feedback" source="sn_hiring_feedback">817f729837831300a128036973990e47</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Hiring Feedback">817f729837831300a128036973990e47</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_9e4ceca5532433004dc0ddeeff7b12e6</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-04-01 09:21:03</sys_updated_on><template/><when>before</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=9e4ceca5532433004dc0ddeeff7b12e6"/></record_update>

	}
	
})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-02-25 09:01:26</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>1ab04dda0f3723007e1763cda8767e1b</sys_id><sys_mod_count>7</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Register Public User</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Hiring Feedback" source="sn_hiring_feedback">817f729837831300a128036973990e47</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Hiring Feedback">817f729837831300a128036973990e47</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_1ab04dda0f3723007e1763cda8767e1b</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-03-20 06:40:46</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=1ab04dda0f3723007e1763cda8767e1b"/></record_update>
